# functionality

## basic todoItem fns

- [ ] init a new todo list
    - create new json file in current directory
- [ ] add a todo to the list
    - due date
    - priority
    - adding contexts and projects to app
    - linking contexts and projects
- [ ] complete a todo
- [ ] archive a todo
- [ ] delete a todo
- [ ] edit a todo

